---
// Expertise Section - Tactile & Clean
---
<section id="services" class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4 tracking-tight">Expertise & Capabilities</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">I focus on building things that actually matter to your business. No fluff, just results-driven engineering and design.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-light/30 hover:bg-white hover:border-primary/20 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,98,254,0.05)] transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Software Engineering</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Scaling businesses with Laravel, Next.js, and robust system architecture. Optimized for performance and long-term maintainability.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-light/30 hover:bg-white hover:border-primary/20 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,98,254,0.05)] transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Experience Design</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Creating digital experiences that people enjoy using. Focus on UI/UX that converts visitors into loyal customers through clarity.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="group p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-light/30 hover:bg-white hover:border-primary/20 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,98,254,0.05)] transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Creative Strategy</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Beyond just code. I help you find your voice through high-quality video content, brand identity, and data-backed digital growth.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>